featured_reviews.review_id:
Went to Home Depot to purchase a new fridge. Start to finish, it was quick and easy. They have a wide selection to choose from.

The only down side was when we received our Fridge, there was 2 small dents; one on each side of the french doors.
Sid Moosavi, that works in appliances was the one that helped us from the time of purchase. He was very helpful and resolved the issue immediately.

I enjoyed the experience of purchasing with Home Depot.
10/10 would recommend and will definitely purchase at this location again.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Your service is garbage. Why post items as available both in-store and/or online when they are not available for either?

I went to the store and could not find what I needed, I was told the computer showed 3 in store but they could not find them. I was advised other stores have it and that I should look for it elsewhere.

I purchased a circular saw online for store pick up the next day and my order was accepted but the next day it was cancelled. The next day, I online purchased a tool kit (offered on the website for delivery) and I paid extra for same-day delivery. Again my order was accepted and later it was cancelled. I guess I'll keep my money then!

Why offer products and services you can not provide. Just mark them as unavailable everywhere and don't waste anyone's time.

featured_reviews.review_id:
I was really disappointed with the level of customer service on three separate visits. All visits were for the same thing. I had come in to purchase a toilet and the new bathroom vanity sink and have them both installed by Home Depot.

My first visit a few weeks ago, no one seemed available to help me. As it was just to ask a few questions and I had already looked at the items on the shelves, I wasn't too concerned , thinking I would just come back at another time.

Then a little over a week ago, I came in and desperately tried to get staff to help me upstairs, but I got the "not my department" response. With one kid simply waving and saying " over there and saying I can't help you you've got to talk to somebody over there". In fact, he was pretty rude about it.

at this point since I couldn't reach the person in Kitchen and bathroom design, I thought I would try emailing her. - I found her card on her desk in the kitchen and bathroom design section. Regrettably, she did not respond to my email  nor my phone call. So I escalated to management.

I got a callback from a manager and he set up an appointment for this past Friday which I took time off work for. He even said that he would pop up to the department to make sure everything went smoothly.

So on Friday I showed up at the 2 o'clock scheduled appointment  only to find that both the person I was supposed to meet and the assistant manager.we're both off that day.

I'm done with Home Depot.

featured_reviews.review_id:
One individual stood out among the rest - Scott, whose exceptional customer service skills shone through at Home Depot's Henning location.

When I couldn't find the desired 24" x 48" corrugated plastic sheets due to their unavailability, Scott came to my rescue. Despite only having larger 48" x 96" sheets in stock, he willingly offered to cut one in half for me, even though I didn't have any tools with me. Scott's helpfulness was refreshing, especially after encountering three other unhelpful employees. As my young daughter astutely pointed out, Scott was the only staff member who made us feel truly welcome.

The management team at Home Depot should acknowledge and appreciate employees like Scott, as his outstanding customer service sets an example for his peers to follow.

featured_reviews.review_id: Have a great experience at this location . The manager Yak was very nice and knowledgeable. His team was very helpful. I have been looking for a patio set for a while but couldn't find anything I like. Once I saw this set , I fell in love and wanted it in my home right away . My car was too small to fit the big box , Yak was able to arrange fast shipping, and I was able to get it the next day . I was not sure about this set, and Yak gave me his honest opinion. The set is high quality  and very comfortable.  I love it.  Thank you, Yak and his team.  Highly recommend homedepot, especially this location.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Rented a sander and my experience was less than expectations. they did not add a required extension cord (different connection), didn't answer the phone, told me to come back to get the extension cord and seemed completely indifferent to my plight. I talked to the store manager who also seemed indifferent and was offered $30 off for my time. I lost half a day running around so the offer was basically not to charge me for the time they wasted on me. Might be an anomaly, make sure you have been given all parts before leaving store.

Edit/update. Hey HD. Your training program is awful. 4 people trying to help me buy a hot water tank and get install. 30 minutes later, I ask about my pro points and they say they don't know. I will check with some other places since I left without being asked to pay for anything.

featured_reviews.review_id: Worst customer service. How much you can be rude to the customer paying a couple of thousands dollars....Many staff there but all of them are busy all the time. You ask for assistance and every time they say wait for a minutes then never show up. I have to ask 3-4 different staffs and if you are lucky, you'll get help after waiting for at least 30 minutes. Usually I never post bad reviews but I'm really upset that staff cut my baseboard wrong size yesterday. This guy( bold head, rude) don't even listen to you carefully when I was telling him the size of cuts. Now what? I have to go back to customer service and explain what happen for refund and redone another cut? How much I have to waste my time to get my job done with this Home Depot.I  spend so much money but this Home Depot screw you up.

featured_reviews.review_id: Customer service manager Jazz and staff Simran at Store #7043 helped me a lot today. Simran was really patient and kind, She listened me very carefully and provided me solutions to my problem. Her working attitude was serious, and she made me feeling warm and CARED! Jazz is a wonderful customer service manager. He was patient too and reliable! I was a little disappointed with the product i purchased But my experience today made me trust the Home Depot! I will choose the Home Depot again!
